      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Choose Zurich for Your Relocation?</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Global Financial Center</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Home to major banks, insurance companies, and financial institutions offering exceptional career opportunities.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Highest Quality of Life</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Consistently ranked among the world's most livable cities with excellent infrastructure and services.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">International Hub</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Diverse, multilingual environment with strong expat community and international schools.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
